flowRoot.flowPara: While preparing the slides for my presentation, XRandr worked but LibreOffice refused to use both monitor outputs. Thanks to E17 I could unset 'full screen window' and move it to the other desktop

Thank you for joining us at the openSUSE Conference 2013 in Thessaloniki. We would like to thank the local team for spending countless hours in preparing the event and all others that pitched in from all corners of the world. Over the next 3 days we will have more than 60 talks, workshops and BoF sessions to keep all Geekos busy, happy and interested. Have a lot of Fun!
The Geeko on the window was made on Thursday afternoon out of 423 Post-It notes and it is the biggest Post-It Geeko we've ever made! ?
